text: Jaroszówka may refer to the following places in Poland: *Jaroszówka, a district of the city of Białystok (NE Poland) *Jaroszówka, Lower Silesian Voivodeship (south-west Poland) *Jaroszówka, Łódź Voivodeship (central Poland) *Jaroszówka, Lesser Poland Voivodeship (south Poland)
title: Jaroszówka
